    "encrypted": "false",
    "long_instructions": "\r\n\r\n#### Code.org has partnered with several **learning management systems** (LMS) to integrate your class rosters with Code.org sections. Each LMS requires a different setup, detailed below.\r\n\r\n## Which LMSs integrate with Code.org?\r\n\r\n<img src=\"https://images.code.org/0fcb66fa9198d4fb5eee8c620ecb18ae-image-1719962626183.23.40 PM.png\" alt=\"Google Classroom, Canvas, Schoology, and Clever logos\">\r\n\r\n#### Currently, Code.org has integrations with **Google Classroom**, **Clever**, **Schoology**, and **Canvas**.\r\n\r\n## How can I sync my LMS with Code.org?\r\n\r\n#### Our Help Center provides robust resources for LMS syncing. Check out the pages below:\r\n\r\n<details style=\"background-color: #ececec; padding: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; border: 1px solid transparent; border-radius: 5px;\">\r\n<summary style=\"font-size: 16px; font-weight: bold;\">Google Classroom</summary>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-left: 20px; margin-right: 20px;\">\r\n<p style=\"font-size: 16px;\"> \r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n <a href=\"https://support.code.org/hc/en-us/articles/115001319312-Setting-Up-Sections-with-Google-Classroom-Sync\" target=\"blank\" rel=\"noopener referrer\">Setting Up Sections with Google Classroom Sync</a>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n<a href=\"https://support.code.org/hc/en-us/articles/360049865752-How-do-I-assign-work-to-my-students-via-Google-Classroom\" target=\"blank\" rel=\"noopener referrer\">Assigning Work to Students via Google Classroom</a>\r\n\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n<a href=\"https://support.code.org/hc/en-us/articles/6496495212557-Troubleshooting-common-issues-with-Google-Classroom-Clever-sections\" target=\"blank\" rel=\"noopener referrer\">Troubleshooting common issues with Google Classroom / Clever sections</a>\r\n\r\n</ul>\r\n</details>\r\n\r\n<details style=\"background-color: #ececec; padding: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; border: 1px solid transparent; border-radius: 5px;\">\r\n<summary style=\"font-size: 16px; font-weight: bold;\">Clever</summary>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n<a href=\"https://support.code.org/hc/en-us/articles/115002716111-Setting-Up-Sections-with-Clever-Sync\" target=\"blank\" rel=\"noopener referrer\">Setting Up Sections with Clever Sync</a>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n<a href=\"https://support.code.org/hc/en-us/articles/6496495212557-Troubleshooting-common-issues-with-Google-Classroom-Clever-sections\" target=\"blank\" rel=\"noopener referrer\">Troubleshooting common issues with Google Classroom / Clever sections</a>\r\n</ul>\r\n</details>\r\n\r\n<details style=\"background-color: #ececec; padding: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; border: 1px solid transparent; border-radius: 5px;\">\r\n<summary style=\"font-size: 16px; font-weight: bold;\">Canvas</summary>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n<a href=\"https://support.code.org/hc/en-us/articles/23621973451405-Create-and-sync-rosters-with-Canvas\" target=\"blank\" rel=\"noopener referrer\">Create and sync rosters with Canvas</a>\r\n</ul>\r\n</details>\r\n<details style=\"background-color: #ececec; padding: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; border: 1px solid transparent; border-radius: 5px;\">\r\n<summary style=\"font-size: 16px; font-weight: bold;\">Schoology</summary>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n<a href=\"https://support.code.org/hc/en-us/articles/23622036958093-Create-and-sync-rosters-with-Schoology\" target=\"blank\" rel=\"noopener referrer\">Create and sync rosters with Schoology</a>\r\n</ul>\r\n</details>\r\n\r\n\r\n"
  },
